A RESOLUTION
1 Commending the Payne-Corley House; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, established in 1998, the Payne-Corley House has become one of the Atlanta
3 area's Highest Rated Wedding Venues and has earned recognition as the top wedding venue
4 in the Duluth area on The Knot, the world's largest wedding site; and
5 WHEREAS, this esteemed venue has further been named Best of Gwinnett for 20 years and
6 is a proud member of The Knot's prestigious "Hall of Fame" for its consistent excellence in
7 wedding services; and
8 WHEREAS, originally built in 1873, the Payne-Corley House is a shining example of
9 historic preservation, with the restored farmhouse lovingly maintained to preserve its
10 Southern charm while offering modern amenities and a romantically historic sense of place;
11 and
12 WHEREAS, the house and gardens have been thoughtfully integrated to provide both indoor
13 and outdoor settings for events of all kinds, including social gatherings, corporate functions,
14 and especially weddings; and
